Find the Windows downloads section. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/3/37/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-3Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-3Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/3/37/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-3Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Find the TeamSpeak Server. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b3/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-3Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-3Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/b/b3/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-3Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Start downloading. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/69/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-3Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-3Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/6/69/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-3Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

If you would like to create an icon on the desktop, leave Create a desktop icon checked and click Next. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c9/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-14Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-14Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/c/c9/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-14Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

If you would like to not create an icon on the desktop, uncheck Create a desktop icon and click Next. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/f/fa/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-14Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-14Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/f/fa/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-14Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

If you would like to launch TeamSpeak right away, Click Finish. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/6b/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-17Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-17Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/6/6b/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-17Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

If you don’t want to launch TeamSpeak right away, uncheck Launch TeamSpeak 2 Server, Click Finish. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/84/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-17Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-17Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/8/84/Install-a-Teamspeak-Server-on-Windows-Step-17Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":570,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}
